# c/MessageEntitySubs

ApproxDuration: ""
DependsOn: "c/MessageSystem, c/Entity"

# Description

[c/EntitySubs: Skills, Items, Effects. Are stored in Entity and are ticked by Entity]
[c/MessageSender: class who can store messages for later polling] // for example MessageContainer
[Game: Unit who stores the Entities and process their Messages]

(Sub)Entity, Skills, Items, Effects : MessageSender

Entity can store Messages for later polling.
After an Entity ticked an EntitySub the entity polls the messages from this EntitySub and stores these messages like an own message.

